Cara install Armbian di STB B860H versi 2

PERSIAPAN
1. Software Belena Etcher (https://etcher.balena.io/)
2. Sofware Bootcard Maker
3. Image Armbian
4. MicroSD 
5. Patch bootloader

PROSES INSTALL ARMBIAN
1. Install Belena Etcher
2. Masukkan MicroSD 
3. Jalankan Belena Ether
4. Pilih Image Armbian
5. Pilih MicroSD
6. Klik Flash
7. Tunggu hingga proses selesai
8. Cabut MicroSD dan tancapkan lagi

PROSES INSTALL BOOTLOADER
1. Jalankan Bootcard Maker
2. Pilih uboot.bin
3. Jangan centang format
4. Format
5. Copy 3 path bootloader file ke MicroSD




